title: Suspicious Encoded PowerShell Execution
id: 5f3d3211-1c32-4e92-9571-002f232ee2bb
status: stable
description: Detects execution of PowerShell with encoded commands, hidden windows, or execution policy bypasses frequently used in delivery cradles.
author: Detection Engineer Specialist
date: 2026/06/28
tags:
    - attack.execution
    - attack.t1059.001
logsource:
    product: windows
    category: process_creation
detection:
    selection:
        Image|endswith:
            - '\powershell.exe'
            - '\pwsh.exe'
        CommandLine|contains:
            - ' -enc'
            - ' -encodedcommand'
            - ' -e '
            - ' -w hidden'
            - ' -windowstyle hidden'
            - ' -nop'
            - ' -noni'
    condition: selection
falsepositives:
    - Administrative management scripts or automated software deployment agents (e.g., SCCM, Intune, RMM tools).
level: high